+    // df/ddf vs IQ-TREE's own computeLikelihoodDerv). Both run once per process; pure read-only diagnostics.
+    // G.4.2: skip the G.2.x one-shot cross-checks under --jolt — ModelFinder is across-model OpenMP-parallel
